{"tid":1419141,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"前線要增加小隊 - 收山小隊","createTime":"2019-08-06T00:00:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T02:26:35.000Z","uid":93137,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"32859b0f7b7255707f7137e8af89df985adb9f5a","tid":1419141,"uid":93137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:00:13.000Z","msg":"發夢個夢境好真實，好嬲！<br />\n琴晚黃大仙報夢比我。<br />\n<br />\n佢話：<br />\n<br />\n元朗鄉黑犬事件，政府將全部白衫釋放曬。<br />\n琴晚荃灣北角又出深紅共狗組織，好多前線手足同埋街坊受傷。久唔久有人揸車岀嚟撞示威者。但係對家有乜野損失？有嘅，比連登仔笑垃圾，比人打幾下。<br />\n<br />\n比著我做對家，下次都會繼續玩，打到示威者仆街。反正零傷害，又有錢收。<br />\n<br />\n所以，我地要有收山小隊！捉到各類鄉黑警犬就打斷佢手腳，等佢受應有嘅懲罰。<br />\n<br />\n前題係要我地受到生命威脅之下，先可以行動。一般藍絲唔需要岀手，屌走佢打佢一獲就可以。"},{"pid":"178127552bee78f5a4b6af682d8a7afd6905fe11","tid":1419141,"uid":282747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:01:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f6d31a3299a1257bc8f4a2850513df7d4b640313","tid":1419141,"uid":93137,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:04:04.000Z","msg":"拗斷手？重擊菠蓋？"},{"pid":"e240fc809cee55a2868c8d988cfe062f5bae2c0b","tid":1419141,"uid":224323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:10:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d0df5136e5abde483f3ec7dc6d468e2f21d29b0","tid":1419141,"uid":93137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:22:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a67c80949e0712cfd5b71ba94abc44fb5c13a77","tid":1419141,"uid":93137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:35:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b99cab627405542a49abe812af05ccbded03a97","tid":1419141,"uid":138934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:55:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0fceb40e14ada9bbfd4c884178c952744faa7db8","tid":1419141,"uid":24523,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:56:04.000Z","msg":"捉到之後扭斷手腳跟住就走人由得佢死"},{"pid":"9a7f2bde2ffe750e58d0e1e926dd9023228a55eb","tid":1419141,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:57:45.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"1a362583651cb9cf13a47c94d98a2042aa235461","tid":1419141,"uid":212436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:10:31.000Z","msg":"打斷腳"},{"pid":"e8374ef4deb437aceb9903bfa00f46aeec5e4379","tid":1419141,"uid":93137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fceb40e14ada9bbfd4c884178c952744faa7db8","tid":1419141,"uid":24523,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:56:04.000Z","msg":"捉到之後扭斷手腳跟住就走人由得佢死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:13:42.000Z","msg":"無錯 打完就走"},{"pid":"f8e1a74552f81c3b6f55f1246c68ca0f69ce14d3","tid":1419141,"uid":14510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:14:46.000Z","msg":"屈鳩斷佢全部手指"},{"pid":"743a5de3cc89a74820503c074ecf1af3331931df","tid":1419141,"uid":42487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:17:04.000Z","msg":"前線好似比較少意識開傘陣<br />\n鏡頭下咁光明正大唔係咁好丫嘛<br />\n周到好撚大罪 勇還勇 但要識保護自己同手足PLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c98bdc0ab5ed90aead96c13c60250acb89e5e835","tid":1419141,"uid":23418,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:19:10.000Z","msg":"算吧啦。現場和理非左膠會制止你，仲扮好心為前線著想，為鄉黑著想。反擊又唔係佢地，比人反擊又唔係佢地，前線自己決定點做就最好。"},{"pid":"ef5249055dc52a2b90807ad1c92f8c1fad1b84d3","tid":1419141,"uid":116723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:28:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9973a878e26230611dacc19eebabf86bccdb354","tid":1419141,"uid":93137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"743a5de3cc89a74820503c074ecf1af3331931df","tid":1419141,"uid":42487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:17:04.000Z","msg":"前線好似比較少意識開傘陣<br />\n鏡頭下咁光明正大唔係咁好丫嘛<br />\n周到好撚大罪 勇還勇 但要識保護自己同手足PLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T0